author: jleroux
msg: While working on OFBIZ-4978, I changed for getDependentDropdownValues.js to load values unselected instead of loading them all selected one by one, then only the last being selected. This was actually a bug and I already wondered why the list had the last option selected by default instead of the 1st. This fixes this last aspect.
